  questionnaire app from a generic look to a more polished and calming
  experience. The agent initiated a comprehensive redesign, starting with a new
  sleep-themed color palette and custom utility classes. Key UI components like
  checkboxes, radio buttons, sliders, and progress bars were enhanced with
  improved visual feedback and transitions. The main questionnaire form and all
  its sections, including the intro and report, were updated to reflect the new
  theme, featuring decorative backgrounds, consistent card styling, and refined
  typography. During the process, a console error related to  values in
  input fields was identified and fixed by modifying the  component to
  safely handle such values. Finally, based on a detailed code-based aesthetic
  review, further refinements were made to alert colors and section border
  opacity to ensure complete visual consistency and professionalism.
